<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<!--
This manifest is a locally-hosted and modified version of https://cpetestutility.stb.r53.xcal.tv/VideoTestStream/main.mpd

Modifications:
- Add BaseURL, to specify the location of the segments (manifest is hosted locally)
- Remove all audio languages except English (test isn't interested in these)
- Split the single period from the original main.mpd into multiple periods to simulate ad breaks, as below:

Period 0 "Preroll" ad     0 - 20s
Period 1 Main asset      20 - 130s
Period 2 "Midroll" ad   130 - 150s
Period 3 "Midroll" ad   150 - 170s
Period 4 Main asset     170 - 280s
Period 5 "Postroll" ad  280 - 310s

Note that the audio track for each period is slightly longer than the video track, due to the differing audio and video segment durations,
but this should be irrelevant since this manifest is used for trickplay, only (test_8003_1).
-->
